OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Comedian Trevor Noah has announced he  
OL,6, is standing down as host of the Daily  
OL,7, Show.                                  
OL,9,FIn a video message, he said was "filled
OL,10,Fwith gratitude for the journey" but    
OL,11,Fthat there was "another part of my life
OL,12,Fthat I want to carry on exploring".    
OL,14,FThe 38-year-old has hosted the show    
OL,15,Fsince taking over from Jon Stewart in  
OL,16,F2015.                                  
OL,18,FHe said the timing of his departure    
OL,19,Fwould be announced later and that he   
OL,20,Fwould continue as host in the meantime.
